---
// src/components/LocationSection.astro
---
<section class="location-section">
  <div class="container split-layout reverse-mobile stretch-layout">
    <div class="image-wrapper balance-height">
      <img src="/fotoPizzeria.webp" alt="Local Pizzas A Todo Gas" class="local-photo color-always">
      <div class="badge-delivery">
          <span class="icon-spacing"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 13a2 2 0 1 1 0 4 2 2 0 0 1 0-4Z"/><path d="M5 13a2 2 0 1 1 0 4 2 2 0 0 1 0-4Z"/><path d="M12 12v3"/><path d="M19 12h-3l-2.2-4.5a2 2 0 0 0-1.8-1.1H8.5a2 2 0 0 0-1.8 1.1L5 11h3"/><path d="M5 11v1"/></svg></span> 
          Reparto a Domicilio
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="action-content">
      <h2 class="section-title">¿EN CASA O <span class="text-accent">AQUÍ?</span></h2>
      <p>Ven a disfrutar del ambiente en nuestro local o llámanos y te llevamos el sabor artesano directamente a tu sofá.</p>
      <div class="action-buttons">
        <a href="tel:+34654843625" class="action-card pulse-animation">
          <div class="icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg></div>
          <div class="info"><span class="small">Llámanos al</span><span class="big">654 84 36 25</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://maps.google.com" target="_blank" class="action-card">
          <div class="icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg></div>
          <div class="info"><span class="small">Ven a vernos</span><span class="big">CÓMO LLEGAR</span></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section { position: relative; width: 100%; }
  .section-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .text-accent { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .location-section { padding: 100px 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; }
  .stretch-layout { align-items: stretch; }
  .image-wrapper { position: relative; min-height: 450px; }
  .local-photo.color-always { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
  .badge-delivery { position: absolute; bottom: 30px; right: -20px; background: var(--color-accent); color: #000; padding: 15px 30px; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 50px; font-family: var(--font-heading); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.1rem; z-index: 5; }
  .action-content { padding-left: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
  .action-buttons { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .action-card { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 25px; padding: 25px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.3s ease; text-decoration: none; }
  .action-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: var(--color-accent); transform: translateX(10px); }
  .action-card .icon { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .action-card .info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .action-card .small { color: var(--color-stone-grey); font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .action-card .big { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.1; }
  .action-card:hover .big { color: var(--color-accent); }
  @keyframes pulse-yellow { 0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.4); } 70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0); } 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(255, 193, 7, 0); } }
  .pulse-animation { animation: pulse-yellow 2s infinite; border-color: var(--color-accent); }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
    .reverse-mobile { display: flex; flex-direction: column-reverse; }
    .image-wrapper { min-height: 250px; height: 300px; }
    .action-content { padding-left: 0; }
    .action-card { justify-content: flex-start; text-align: left; }
    .badge-delivery { right: 50%; transform: translateX(50%); bottom: -20px; white-space: nowrap; }
  }
</style>